The '''Red Hills Clan''' was a [[Witches of Dathomir|Dathomiri Witch]] clan based around the [[Red Hills/Legends|Red Hills]] on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]]. [[Augwynne Djo]] sent a messenger to the clan in [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], asking for support against the [[Nightsisters/Legends|Nightsisters]]. After the [[Battle of Dathomir (Hunt for Zsinj)|battle of Dathomir]], the clan sent a representative to the Sisters of the [[Singing Mountain Clan]] to celebrate the victory over the Nightsisters.<ref name="CPL">''[[The Courtship of Princess Leia]]''</ref>

